  "remarks": "Evraz PLC is a UK-based company that is leading in the steel and mining industries, with its core business taking place in the Russian Federation. Therefore, Evraz PLC is involved in an economic sector providing a substantial source of revenue to the Government of the Russian Federation, which is responsible for the annexation of Crimea and the destabilisation of Ukraine.",
